    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation evidence from FDA benchmark pump demonstrates CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within acceptable tolerance across the CPB operating range. Model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission.",
